OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,FA new range of qualifications to help
OL,7,Fsecondary learners will be available
OL,8,Falong with new Made-for-Wales GCSEs by
OL,9,F2027.
OL,11,FThe decision made by Qualification
OL,12,FWales will see introduction of new-
OL,13,Fwork related VCSEs (Vocational
OL,14,FCertificate of Secondary Education)
OL,15,Fand new skills-based qualifications.
OL,17,FThe aim is to provide all secondary
OL,18,Flearners with innovative, exciting,
OL,19,Finclusive and new qualifications that
OL,20,Fmeet the purpose of the Curriculum for
OL,21,FWales.
