OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,FCassy Taylor, director of
OL,7,Fqualifications policy and reform at
OL,8,FQualifications Wales, said this new
OL,9,Fpolicy represents the "biggest
OL,10,Ftransformation of 14-16 qualifications
OL,11,Fin a generation".
OL,13,FShe stated: "It will mean that all
OL,14,Flearners, whatever their interest,
OL,15,Faptitude or ability, will be able to
OL,16,Fgain recognition and reward for what
OL,17,Fthey know, understand and can do.
