OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,F"Armed with these new qualifications,
OL,7,Fthey'll be able to progress from the
OL,8,FCurriculum for Wales to the next stage
OL,9,Fof learning and form a basis for their
OL,10,Fown personal success."
OL,12,FThe changes will affect the secondary
OL,13,Fschool learners across the country.
