OL,6,FAlong with new Made-for-Wales GCSEs,
OL,7,Flearners in Wales aged 14-16 will be
OL,8,Fable to choose from:
OL,10,FPersonal Project qualificationSpeaking
OL,11,Fto ITV Wales, Rhyl High headteacher
OL,12,FClaire Armistead said the new
OL,13,Fcurriculum will help children become
OL,14,F"whole-rounded human beings" able to
OL,15,Fgo in the direction that "best suits
OL,16,Fthem".
OL,18,FShe continued: "I think we're
OL,19,Feducating humans now, not just a type
OL,20,Fof child. We want all parts of that
OL,21,Fhuman to be valued equally.
