OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,F"Some children are very academic and
OL,7,Fthose children can find a quick route
OL,8,Fto university. The problem was, our
OL,9,Fqualifications, our education system
OL,10,Fwas already out of date and written by
OL,11,Fadults who didn't know what children
OL,12,Fwould need in the future.
OL,14,F"So with the new curriculum, we need
OL,15,Fto make sure that every child and all
OL,16,Ftheir skills, are equally valued."
