OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,FShe added: "It's about finding what
OL,7,Fchildren can thrive in and giving them
OL,8,Fthose opportunities and then
OL,9,Facknowledging them and rewarding them.
OL,10,FThey're not lesser or more than each
OL,11,Fother, they're just different."
OL,13,FBen Cottam, head of Wales for the
OL,14,FFederation of Small Businesses, said
OL,15,F"Developing skills for the future is
OL,16,Fof the utmost importance for the
OL,17,Ffuture workforce in Wales".
