OL,3,CVCSES: What are they and what can 14-
OL,4,C16-year-olds expect?
OL,6,FHe added: "Small businesses
OL,7,Fconsistently raise access to skills as
OL,8,Fa barrier to growth. Our research
OL,9,Ftells us that closer links between
OL,10,Fproviders, the business community, and
OL,11,Fteaching institutions, can really
OL,12,Fbenefit learner outcomes, as well as
OL,13,Fsupport businesses in harnessing the
OL,14,Fright skills to grow, and thus
OL,15,Fbolstering local economies.
OL,17,F"It is our hope that the new National
OL,18,F14-6 Qualifications offer will go some
OL,19,Fway to improve choices for learners.
